{"tid":2068750,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拆僭建揭「不存在的3號」 陶輝霸鄰屋 通道做浴室","createTime":"2020-06-18T02:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T03:23:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d407ae4df774d2d51ee78e3173461a03c9736c3d","tid":2068750,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T02:10:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200618/UMVSELFHMFBUI52QGJHVTH5YYU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200618%2FUMVSELFHMFBUI52QGJHVTH5YYU%2F&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=dfaf3382\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200618%2FUMVSELFHMFBUI52QGJHVTH5YYU%2F&h=f93b6701\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200618/UMVSELFHMFBUI52QGJHVTH5YYU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n拆僭建揭「不存在的3號」<br />\n陶輝霸鄰屋 通道做浴室<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TWSQ4JKFQ6VVWLOGARC53FEBBQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTWSQ4JKFQ6VVWLOGARC53FEBBQ.gif&h=8f73bd7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩屋之間的通道被清空後，可見花灑頭（紅圈示）等設施，顯示通道曾被裝成浴室，1號屋及3號屋均設有門口與該處相連（箭嘴示），足證兩屋曾被打通。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警務處助理處長陶輝（Rupert Dover）及其警長妻子張雅詩被揭發涉多項違規，地政總署早前證實，兩人居住的碧水新村1號牌照屋涉僭建及霸佔官地，須一個月內糾正。本報發現，原來陶輝亦涉嫌擴建及霸佔毗鄰的3號屋，並將1號屋與3號屋之間的通道改為浴室使用，有關位置、以及1號屋僭建的天台近日開始清拆。<br />\n<br />\n本報4月揭發陶輝夫婦。。。。。。。。。。。。。。具，現時天台屋已拆除，天台範圍堆滿木板及窗框等建築廢料。<br />\n<br />\n除1號屋天台外，。。。。。。。。。。。。。貨車運送泥頭廢料。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2TPPVENVHQEVEXF6OZ5565TTCU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2TPPVENVHQEVEXF6OZ5565TTCU.gif&h=94b693e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陶輝夫婦所居住及霸佔的牌照屋已開始清拆僭建物。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本報查詢逾月 地署未回覆<br />\n<br />\n早前有消息指，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。的磚牆亦與一般浴室使用的磁磚相似。無論1號屋或3號屋均設門口與涉事「浴室」相連，反映兩屋曾被打通。<br />\n<br />\n地政總署2019年1月曾在3號屋外貼出通告，已刪除碧水新村3號的寮屋登記，原因是有關寮屋的構築物已不存在或已被清拆。至於為何現時3號屋仍有建築物、1號屋及3號屋是否打通、陶輝有否佔用3號屋等情況，本報自5月1日起，多次向地政總署查詢，惟至今逾一個月，該署仍未有任何回覆。本報早前已按《公開資料守則》向地政總署公開資料主任索取有關資料。<br />\n<br />\n至於另一間被陶輝夫婦包裝成民宿出租的61A號屋，早前同樣被證實僭建及違規居住，地政總署早前亦已發信勒令限期前糾正。"},{"pid":"d656a7e2154b95bd5df1caed3ad38bcf25b8c1e6","tid":2068750,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T02:11:05.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"8ef27dc140247a9ca8f582423a53d0c1e74a8831","tid":2068750,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T02:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f69088135405dc90b571785ca1df125c6d8f6b3","tid":2068750,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T02:36:58.000Z","msg":"有特權怕乜，霸埋成條街都仲得"},{"pid":"4604aeb738191148d9f0b4ea260dcba4988018a5","tid":2068750,"uid":91422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T02:42:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44a1f170ef2e210bedafc3b336687fe790ea9022","tid":2068750,"uid":165127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T02:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5feb75b0353a80a02d0236d61438039bd3ee1e","tid":2068750,"uid":76899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T02:57:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab652b3551e5d66b835e293c1f565b3e991c42a8","tid":2068750,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:01:21.000Z","msg":"其實好撚多<br />\n地政又唔管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n霸來自用唔理<br />\n長租俾人又唔理<br />\n霸隔離，再霸隔離，成排霸晒<br />\n<br />\n係霸做旅館無旅館牌先做野"},{"pid":"36c12a20a3c32830c35ca84b6e149666be25740b","tid":2068750,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:17:47.000Z","msg":"Tuii"},{"pid":"6d65ea904434c834ce8c50e90d4d0354c2793342","tid":2068750,"uid":39200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:23:06.000Z","msg":"遲D調到去東廠, 地政班人等住送哂上支那啦"}]}